<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>ELR</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&family=DM+Mono:wght@300;400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    background: #ffffff;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    min-height: 100vh;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    position: relative;
    background: #ffffff;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-deco {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 50%;
    opacity: 0.22;
  }
  .deco1 { width: 420px; height: 420px; background: #c8f230; top: -80px; left: -120px; }
  .deco2 { width: 280px; height: 280px; background: #c0c0c0; bottom: 20px; right: -60px; }
  .deco3 { width: 120px; height: 120px; background: #a8e000; top: 60px; right: 100px; }

  .badge {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    background: #1a1a1a;
    color: #c8f230;
    padding: 5px 14px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(5rem, 20vw, 10rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 0.9;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .hero-tagline {
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: #707070;
    max-width: 340px;
    line-height: 1.9;
  }

  .scroll-hint {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 2rem;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #a0a0a0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
  }
  .scroll-line {
    width: 1px;
    height: 32px;
    background: #c8f230;
    animation: scrollpulse 1.6s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes scrollpulse { 0%,100%{opacity:1} 50%{opacity:0.3} }

  section {
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
    max-width: 860px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #a0a0a0;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .section-label::after {
    content: '';
    flex: 1;
    height: 1px;
    background: #e0e0e0;
  }

  .facts-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1px;
    background: #d8d8d8;
    border: 1px solid #d8d8d8;
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .fact-card {
    background: #ffffff;
    padding: 2rem 1.75rem;
  }

  .fact-num {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #c8f230;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .fact-text {
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #3a3a3a;
  }

  .hobby-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
    border: 1px solid #d8d8d8;
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hobby-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
    background: #ffffff;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .hobby-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .hobby-row:hover { background: #f5ffe0; }

  .hobby-icon {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: #c8f230;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    font-size: 18px;
  }

  .hobby-name {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }

  .hobby-desc {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #a0a0a0;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-left: auto;
    text-align: right;
  }

  .fav-cols {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .fav-col-head {
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #a0a0a0;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.8rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #c8f230;
  }

  .fav-item {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #3a3a3a;
    padding: 0.4rem 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
    border-bottom: 1px dashed #e8e8e8;
  }
  .fav-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .travel-card {
    background: #1a1a1a;
    color: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 3rem 2.5rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .travel-big {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: #c8f230;
  }

  .travel-place {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .travel-text {
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 2;
    color: #c0c0c0;
  }

  footer {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    background: #f8fff0;
  }

  footer .big-hi {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 10vw, 6rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }

  footer .sub {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #a0a0a0;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  footer .dot {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #c8f230;
    margin: 0 6px;
    vertical-align: middle;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .facts-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .fav-cols { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .travel-card { flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; }
    .hobby-desc { display: none; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-deco deco1"></div>
  <div class="hero-deco deco2"></div>
  <div class="hero-deco deco3"></div>
  <div class="badge">Definitely South African</div>
  <h1>ELR</h1>
  <p class="hero-tagline">Not extroverted. Here to say hi. Knows where the clues are.</p>
  <div class="scroll-hint">
    <span>scroll</span>
    <div class="scroll-line"></div>
  </div>
</div>

<section>
  <div class="section-label">Fun facts</div>
  <div class="facts-grid">
    <div class="fact-card">
      <div class="fact-num">01</div>
      <div class="fact-text">Has been on first dates. Plural. The data collection continues.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="fact-card">
      <div class="fact-num">02</div>
      <div class="fact-text">The birthmark grows back. Every time. Make of that what you will.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="fact-card" style="grid-column: 1 / -1; border-top: 1px solid #d8d8d8;">
      <div class="fact-num">03</div>
      <div class="fact-text">Keeps a mental file on everyone she's ever met. Organised by suspicion level.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section style="padding-top: 0;">
  <div class="section-label">Things I do</div>
  <div class="hobby-list">
    <div class="hobby-row">
      <div class="hobby-icon">🔍</div>
      <div class="hobby-name">Being Nancy Drew</div>
      <div class="hobby-desc">amateur sleuth &amp; enjoyer of clues</div>
    </div>
    <div class="hobby-row">
      <div class="hobby-icon">💃</div>
      <div class="hobby-name">Dancing</div>
      <div class="hobby-desc">in living rooms, mostly</div>
    </div>
    <div class="hobby-row">
      <div class="hobby-icon">📋</div>
      <div class="hobby-name">The rules</div>
      <div class="hobby-desc">knows them, possibly enforces them</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section style="padding-top: 0;">
  <div class="section-label">A few favourites</div>
  <div class="fav-cols">
    <div>
      <div class="fav-col-head">Music</div>
      <div class="fav-item">Enya</div>
      <div class="fav-item">Robyn</div>
      <div class="fav-item">No Doubt</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="fav-col-head">Screen</div>
      <div class="fav-item">The Virgin Suicides</div>
      <div class="fav-item">Midsomer Murders</div>
      <div class="fav-item">Twin Peaks</div>
      <div class="fav-item">Parks &amp; Rec</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="fav-col-head">Reading</div>
      <div class="fav-item">Emily Dickinson poems</div>
      <div class="fav-item" style="color: #a0a0a0; font-style: italic;">Because I could not stop for death...</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section style="padding-top: 0;">
  <div class="section-label">Places</div>
  <div class="travel-card">
    <div class="travel-big">🍜</div>
    <div>
      <div class="travel-place">Cup Noodle Museum</div>
      <div class="travel-text">Dream destination. A whole museum dedicated to instant noodles. Aspirational. Correct.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <div class="big-hi">Hi.</div>
  <p class="sub">That's all. That's the website.<span class="dot"></span>ELR</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
